            "creation_date": 1520589545,
            "body": "<p>A better way would be write your <code>Math.abs()<\/code> method, the code is much cleaner:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public abstract class MathUtils {\n    public static short absShort(short a){\n        return a &gt; 0 ? a : -a;\n    }\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
